      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Déterminer le rayon de convergence et montrer que $f$ vérifie l'équation :\n    $x(4-x)y' - (x+2)y = -2$.",
        "html": "<p>Déterminer le rayon de convergence et montrer que <span class=\"math inline\">\\(f\\)</span> vérifie l’équation : <span class=\"math inline\">\\(x(4-x)y&#39; - (x+2)y = -2\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "c0eb6101-b9df-45ac-9545-4aecf108ff0c",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$R=4$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(R=4\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
